column2: SELECT TOP #  ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY gi.ra ASC) AS Row,  gi.ra, gi.dec, gi.z, gi.z_err, gi.v_disp, gi.v_disp_err,  gl.h_alpha_eqw, gl.h_beta_eqw, gl.h_gamma_eqw, gl.neiii_#_eqw,   gl.oiii_#_eqw, gl.oiii_#_eqw,gl.oi_#_eqw, gl.oii_#_eqw,   gl.oiii_#_eqw, gl.nii_#_eqw, gl.sii_#_eqw,  gl.h_alpha_eqw_err, gl.h_beta_eqw_err, gl.h_gamma_eqw_err,   gl.neiii_#_eqw_err, gl.oiii_#_eqw_err, gl.oiii_#_eqw_err,   gl.oi_#_eqw_err, gl.oii_#_eqw_err,gl.oiii_#_eqw_err,   gl.nii_#_eqw_err, gl.sii_#_eqw_err, gl.h_alpha_flux,   gl.h_beta_flux, gl.h_gamma_flux, gl.neiii_#_flux, gl.oiii_#_flux,   gl.oiii_#_flux,gl.oi_#_flux, gl.oii_#_flux, gl.oiii_#_flux,   gl.nii_#_flux, gl.sii_#_flux, gl.h_alpha_flux_err,   gl.h_beta_flux_err, gl.h_gamma_flux_err, gl.neiii_#_flux_err,   gl.oiii_#_flux_err, gl.oiii_#_flux_err,gl.oi_#_flux_err,   gl.oii_#_flux_err, gl.oiii_#_flux_err, gl.nii_#_flux_err,   gl.sii_#_flux_err FROM galSpecInfo as gi  JOIN galSpecLine AS gl ON gi.specobjid = gl.specobjid
